<hr/>
<div class="row-fluid text-center clearfix">
	<div class="col-md-4 inactive-page">
	<%= link_to '1', cart_path, class: "round" %>
		<span>View Cart</span>
	</div>
	<div class="col-md-4 inactive-page">
	<%= link_to '2', payment_path, class: "round" %>
		<span>Payment</span>
	</div>
	<div class="col-md-4">
		<span class="round active-page">3</span>
		<span>Additional info</span>
	</div>
</div>
<div id="status-box">
	<h1 id="status-header">CONGRATS! YOUR ORDER HAS BEEN PROCESSED</h1>
	<p id="status-content"><i>To get your advice please complete the form below. This can be done now or you can return to it later.</i></p>
</div>
<div class="row-fluid">
	<section class="col-sm-8">
	<div class="info">
    	<legend class="italic-header"><i>Basic Information</i></legend>
    	<form id="basic-info" class="form-inline" role="form">
    	<p>I am looking for a <input type="text" class="form-control input-size" placeholder="product (ex. chair, sofa)" required> for my <input type="text" class="form-control input-size-big" placeholder="room (ex. living room, bedroom)" required> in <input type="text" class="form-control input-size" placeholder="color or materials" required> and my budget is <input type="text" class="form-control input-size" placeholder="price (ex.$500)" required>.</p>
	</div>
    	<p class="add-info">ANY ADDITIONAL INFORMATION SHARE HELPS US GIVE THE BEST RECOMMENDATIONS</p>
		<textarea class="form-control form" rows="4" cols="45" placeholder="Helpful information would be approximate dimensions of the product you're looking for, other items your planning on replacing in your room, materials you prefer, materials or colors you like or do not like, etc." required>
		</textarea>

		<legend id="photos" class="italic-header"><i>Upload Photos</i></legend>
		<p class="small-font">The best photos capture the key features of the room (main furniture, layout, room features) from 2 or 3 corners of the room. Capture key colors, textures and patterns that you want to keep.</p>
		<div id="upload-form">
		<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-picture"></span><br>
			DRAG AND DROP PHOTOS HERE<br>
			OR <a href="#" class="blue-links">SELECT FILE TO UPLOAD</a>
		</div>

		<legend id="photos" class="italic-header"><i>Additional Information <span class="text-muted">(Optional)</span></i></legend>
		<p class="add-info">PASTE A URL FOR A PINTEREST BOARD, HOUZZ IDEA BOOK OR OTHER WEBSITE</p>
		<input type="url" class="form-control input-size-big">
		<p class="add-info">SHARE ONE OF YOUR DECORIST DESIGN BOARD</p>
		<button type="button" class="btn btn-primary button blue-links gray">ATTACH DECORIST DESIGN BOARD</button>
		<div>
		<p class="pull-right">
		  <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary button blue-links gray">SAVE DRAFT</button>
		  <button type="submit button" class="btn btn-primary button">SEND TO DESIGNER</button>
		</p>
		</div>
		</form>
		</section>
		<aside class="col-sm-4">
			 <%= image_tag('image-1.png') %>
		</aside>
</div>